\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527277\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 02, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ery1665702992432.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ery1665702992432.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ery1665702992432.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ery1665702992432\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n Uniface Installation Program\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Uniface installation program prompts you for information that it needs.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ery1665702992432__section_w1750ab1b5b1_w1751ab1b5_w1752ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Information that may be requested</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__1\">\n Requested Information\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Destination</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__2\">\n File system location where Uniface should be installed.\n <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"ery1665702992432__note_w1753ab1b5b1b1b3b7b1b3b1_w1754ab1b5b1b1b3b7b1b3_w1755ab1b5b1b1b3b7b1_w1756ab1b5b1b1b3b7_w1757ab1b5b1b1b3_w1758ab1b5b1b1_w1759ab1b5b1_w1760ab1b5_w1761ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> It is not possible to install over an existing installation.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Components</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__2\">\n Select the products and tools you want to install.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Character set</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__2\">\n Choose the character set or code page appropriate for your language.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Port numbers</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__2\">\n Port numbers to be used for the Uniface Router and Tomcat Web server. The installer checks whether the default port numbers are already in use and suggests the next available port numbers, but you can enter your preferred port numbers.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">License information</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ery1665702992432__table_d5774e1_d5775e1_d5776e1__entry__2\">Select the Sentinel license type, or choose to\n                        manually configure your license later. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mac1665702749697.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Installing Uniface on Unix and Linux</a><p>The Uniface installation program and related files are provided in a .tar file. After extracting the file you can run the Uniface installer.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cgf1665702990991.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface Installer for Windows</a><p>The Uniface installer prompts you for the information it needs, and provides on-screen guidance to help you make the appropriate choices.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527277\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527277\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface Installation Program Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 02, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface Installation Program The Uniface installation program prompts you for information that it needs. Table 1. Information that may be requested Requested Information Description Destination File system location where Uniface should be installed. Note: It is not possible to install over an existing installation. Components Select the products and tools you want to install. Character set Choose the character set or code page appropriate for your language. Port numbers Port numbers to be used for the Uniface Router and Tomcat Web server. The installer checks whether the default port numbers are already in use and suggests the next available port numbers, but you can enter your preferred port numbers. License information Select the Sentinel license type, or choose to manually configure your license later. Related Links Installing Uniface on Unix and Linux The Uniface installation program and related files are provided in a .tar file. After extracting the file you can run the Uniface installer. Uniface Installer for Windows The Uniface installer prompts you for the information it needs, and provides on-screen guidance to help you make the appropriate choices. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}